<p align="center"><font face="Verdana" size="5">EverQuest Chat Session - January 2nd, 2000&nbsp;&nbsp; #1</font></p>


<font face="verdana" size="2">
<p>
<br>
   Lensenor:  Question....why are you stating you are against sale of virtual
        property on ebay...yet probegating the phenomena with all your
        nerfing?&nbsp;<br>
<br>
   <font color="#00FFFF">Aradune:</font>  &lt;r>lens: rofl. nice loaded question there&nbsp;<br>
<br>
   Lensenor:  Well..it's true&nbsp;<br>
<br>
   <font color="#00FFFF">Aradune:</font>  &lt;r>lens: no, its not true. less than 1  of players sell on ebay&nbsp;<br>
<br>
   <font color="#00FFFF">Aradune:</font>  &lt;r>the percent sign doesnt show&nbsp;<br>
<br>
   <font color="#808080">:Aradune sighs</font>&nbsp;<br>
<br>
   a_CERFnet_router02:  We've killed the gods n dragons and noticed there
        were very little caster dropped items. Tanks n such can go around
        carrying "godly" weapons but the 4 main casters get nothing off of them?&nbsp;<br>
<br>
   <font color="#DEB887">GM-Daegarmo:</font>  &lt;r>Router . . . I will bring it up in the meetings&nbsp;<br>
<br>
   a_happy_customer02:  this game rocks!  thanks for making it Aradune!&nbsp;<br>
<br>
   <font color="#00FFFF">Aradune:</font>  &lt;r>thanks happy&nbsp;<br>
<br>
   nembur:  wow it's Aradune!!&nbsp;<br>
<br>
   afnsucks:  I see lots of stuff going on eBay...&nbsp;<br>
<br>
   <font color="#00FFFF">Aradune:</font>  &lt;r>afn: do the math&nbsp;<br>
<br>
   a_happy_customer02:  Aradune - I do have one question, I heard that the
        firey avenger is not in the game, any idea when it will be back? or
        is that a secret?&nbsp;<br>
<br>
   <font color="#00FFFF">Aradune:</font>  &lt;r>happy: this month it will be back&nbsp;<br>
<br>
   Ledskof:  Aradune- a question if i may?... are there any plans to make the
        planes more stable? the general feeling of people I group with find
        them to just be rediculous, the monster behavior and so on&nbsp;<br>
<br>
   <font color="#00FFFF">Aradune:</font>  &lt;r>ledskof: they are supposed to be rediculously hard&nbsp;<br>
<br>
   <font color="#00FFFF">Aradune:</font>  &lt;r>leds: but we are working on better stability&nbsp;<br>
<br>
   Ledskof:  Aradune-- Are you working on greater stability for the planes,
        such as makng it so monsters dont attack through walls, or did you
        mean just greater stabiliity in general?&nbsp;<br>
<br>
   <font color="#00FFFF">Aradune:</font>  &lt;r>led: better stability yes, monsters attacking through some
        walls will never go away&nbsp;<br>
<br>
   <font color="#00FFFF">Aradune:</font>  &lt;r>for NPCs to accurately consider all walls in some zones would
